---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy | Quoter"
  description="How Quoter handles information for roofers and their customers."
>
  <main class="relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-2xl px-6 py-20 sm:py-24">
    <div class="legal-panel rounded-3xl p-7 sm:p-10">
      <a href="/" class="text-[14px] font-medium text-brand-600 hover:underline">&larr; Back to Quoter</a>

      <h1 class="font-display mt-5 text-[clamp(1.9rem,5vw,2.6rem)] leading-[1.05] text-ink">
        Privacy Policy
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-2 text-[13px] text-muted">Last updated: July 2026</p>

      <h2>Who this is for</h2>
      <p>
        Quoter is built for roofing businesses. This policy covers information
        we handle when you use Quoter as a roofer, and when a visitor on your
        website uses the estimate widget.
      </p>

      <h2>What we collect</h2>
      <p>
        To produce an estimate, we use the address a visitor types into the
        widget. Seeing a price does not require a name, phone number, or email.
        If you book a call with us, we collect the contact details you provide
        so we can follow up.
      </p>

      <h2>When someone requests a quote on your site</h2>
      <p>
        If a visitor asks to be contacted after seeing an estimate, we may
        collect contact details so you can follow up. We share those details
        with you as the roofing business running the widget. We do not sell
        that information to other companies.
      </p>

      <h2>What we do not do</h2>
      <p>
        We do not sell personal information. We do not send marketing that
        nobody asked for. We do not pass customer details to unrelated call
        centres.
      </p>

      <h2>Analytics</h2>
      <p>
        We use basic, privacy-respecting analytics to understand how the site
        and product perform, such as page speed measurements. These are not
        meant to identify individual visitors.
      </p>

      <h2>Your choices</h2>
      <p>
        If you want information you have given us removed, email us and we
        will delete it where we can: <a href="mailto:hello@quoter.app" class="text-brand-600 hover:underline">hello@quoter.app</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-panel {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);
    backdrop-filter: blur(20px) saturate(1.3);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px) saturate(1.3);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-float);
  }
  h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 19px;
    color: var(--color-ink);
    margin-top: 1.9rem;
  }
  p {
    margin-top: 0.6rem;
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--color-ink-soft);
  }
</style>
